summary: An ordinance accepting deeds from John Mathies and Helen J. Mathies, his wife; Athlene M. Raymond and Harold C. Raymond, her husband; Charles Grolimund and Lena Grolumund, his wife; A.E. Cross and Harriet M. Cross, his wife; Frank W. Herrick and Mary F. Herrick, his wife; C. Reinhardt and Caroline Reinhardt, his wife; Peter B. Fernandez, a bachelor; and Thomas J. Fox and Gladys M. Fox, his wife; to the City of Seattle, and laying off East 56th Street.
